"use strict";(self.webpackChunkmocpilot_docs=self.webpackChunkmocpilot_docs||[]).push([[2991],{2121:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"archive":{"blogPosts":[{"id":"/2026/01/10/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2026/01/10/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2026-01-10-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2026.1.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.1.0 \u2014 Actualizare de func\u021bii \u0219i stabilitate","date":"2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":1.24,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2026.1.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/12/28/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2026.1.0 \u2014 Actualizare de func\u021bii \u0219i stabilitate\\n\\nSuntem bucuro\u0219i s\u0103 anun\u021b\u0103m lansarea **MOCPilot 2026.1.0**, disponibil\u0103 acum pe **Android**, **iOS** \u0219i **macOS**.\\n\\nAceast\u0103 versiune introduce **modul invitat**, \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021be\u0219te utilizarea pe dispozitive mobile \u0219i aduce corec\u021bii importante de stabilitate \u0219i performan\u021b\u0103 pe toate platformele suportate.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Ce este nou \xeen 2026.1.0?\\n\\n### \ud83c\udd95 Nou\\n- **Mod invitat** \u2014 folose\u0219te aplica\u021bia f\u0103r\u0103 cont, cu op\u021biunea de a crea unul mai t\xe2rziu\\n- Selec\u021bia limbii a fost ad\u0103ugat\u0103 pe ecranul de autentificare\\n- Aplica\u021bia blocheaz\u0103 acum utilizarea hub-urilor cu firmware nesuportat \u0219i afi\u0219eaz\u0103 un avertisment clar\\n\\n### \u2699\ufe0f \xcembun\u0103t\u0103\u021biri\\n- \xcembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit modul de tragere a blocurilor pe mobil (gestionare mai bun\u0103 a atingerii, mai pu\u021bine interac\u021biuni accidentale)\\n- Paleta de blocuri se ascunde acum automat \xeen timpul tragerii pe mobil\\n- Dialogurile de alert\u0103 aplic\u0103 acum un efect de blur pe fundal\\n- \xcembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit\u0103 gestionarea introducerii textului pe toate platformele\\n- Control mai fluent al hub-ului cu laten\u021b\u0103 redus\u0103\\n\\n### \ud83d\udee0 Remedieri\\n- Remediate mai multe probleme de drag & drop, inclusiv blocuri blocate \u0219i pierderea inputului mouse/touch\\n- Remediate crash-uri la oprirea programelor care folosesc blocuri personalizate (\u201eMy\u201d)\\n- Remediat faptul c\u0103 calibrarea rack-ului de direc\u021bie nu revenea la pozi\u021bia central\u0103\\n- Remediat lag-ul la controlul hub-ului \u0219i r\u0103spunsul \xeent\xe2rziat al motorului\\n- Remediate probleme cu porturile editorului, glisoare \u0219i blocurile de valori pentru vitez\u0103\\n- Remediat\u0103 problema dialogului principal \u0219i diverse probleme de layout UI\\n- Traduceri actualizate \u0219i remedieri pentru mici inconsisten\u021be vizuale\\n\\n---\\n\\nActualiza\u021bi MOCPilot la cea mai recent\u0103 versiune \u0219i bucura\u021bi-v\u0103 de o experien\u021b\u0103 mai fluid\u0103, stabil\u0103 \u0219i accesibil\u0103 pe toate dispozitivele."},{"id":"/2025/12/28/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/12/28/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-12-28-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4 \u2014 Actualizare de stabilitate \u0219i experien\u021b\u0103","date":"2025-12-28T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":0.77,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2026.1.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2026/01/10/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/11/15/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4 \u2014 Actualizare de stabilitate \u0219i experien\u021b\u0103\\n\\nSuntem bucuro\u0219i s\u0103 anun\u021b\u0103m lansarea **MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4**, disponibil\u0103 acum pe **Android**, **iOS** \u0219i **macOS**.\\n\\nAceast\u0103 versiune se concentreaz\u0103 pe un **comportament mai fluid**, **fiabilitate \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit\u0103** \u0219i **optimiz\u0103ri ale interfe\u021bei utilizatorului** pe toate platformele.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Ce s-a \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit \xeen versiunile 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4?\\n\\n- Comportament mai fluid \u0219i mai stabil datorit\u0103 logicii temporale \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bite\\n- Sincronizare \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit\u0103 a profilurilor \u0219i fiabilitate mai bun\u0103 a actualiz\u0103rilor\\n- Aspect \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bit al listei de profiluri, cu informa\u021bii mai clare\\n- Efecte vizuale \u0219i interac\u021biune \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bite pentru glisorul de aur\u0103\\n- Corectarea problemelor de inversare pitch/roll \xeen controale\\n- \xcembun\u0103t\u0103\u021biri ale layout-ului UI pe telefoane \u0219i tablete\\n- Corectarea problemelor de culoare, comutatoare \u0219i consisten\u021b\u0103 vizual\u0103\\n- Traduceri \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bite \u0219i consisten\u021b\u0103 mai bun\u0103 a textelor\\n- Corec\u021bii generale de erori, \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021biri de performan\u021b\u0103 \u0219i stabilitate\\n\\n---\\n\\nActualiza\u021bi MOCPilot la cea mai recent\u0103 versiune \u0219i bucura\u021bi-v\u0103 de o experien\u021b\u0103 mai stabil\u0103 \u0219i mai receptiv\u0103 pe toate dispozitivele."},{"id":"/2025/11/15/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/11/15/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-11-15-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 \u2014 Lansare oficial\u0103 multiplatform\u0103!","date":"2025-11-15T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"}],"readingTime":0.49,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0 - 2025.2.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/12/28/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.9","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/06/3/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.2.0 \u2014 Lansare oficial\u0103 multiplatform\u0103!\\n\\nSuntem \xeenc\xe2nta\u021bi s\u0103 anun\u021b\u0103m lansarea oficial\u0103 a **MOCPilot 2025.2.0**, disponibil\u0103 acum pe **Android**, **iOS** \u0219i **macOS**!\\n\\nAplica\u021bia cunoscut\u0103 anterior ca **Controlz** a fost redenumit\u0103 **MOCPilot**, pentru a reflecta mai bine scopul \u0219i direc\u021bia viitoare \u2014 o platform\u0103 unificat\u0103 pentru controlul \u0219i programarea crea\u021biilor LEGO\xae.\\n\\n---\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\n## \u2728 Ce este nou \xeen 2025.2.0?\\n\\n- Lansare unificat\u0103 pentru Android, iOS \u0219i macOS  \\n- Stabilitate, performan\u021b\u0103 \u0219i reac\u021bie UI \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021bite  \\n- Identitate vizual\u0103 actualizat\u0103 \u2013 *MOCPilot*  \\n- Suport continuu pentru LEGO\xae Control+, BuWizz 2/3 \u0219i module Bluetooth personalizate  \\n\\n---\\n\\nDescarc\u0103 MOCPilot \u0219i bucur\u0103-te de o nou\u0103 experien\u021b\u0103 \xeen controlul crea\u021biilor tale LEGO\xae!"},{"id":"/2025/06/3/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/06/3/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-06-3-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.9","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.9 finns nu tillg\xe4nglig p\xe5 Mac App Store!","date":"2025-06-03T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.32,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.9","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.2.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/11/15/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/17/post"}},"content":"import { MacAppStoreBadge } from \'@site/src/pages/\';\\n\\n## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.9 finns nu tillg\xe4nglig p\xe5 Mac App Store!\\n\\nVi \xe4r glada att kunna meddela lanseringen av MOCPilot 2025.1.9 som en native macOS-app!\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\nNu kan du njuta av full prestanda p\xe5 skrivbordet och s\xf6ml\xf6s integration med macOS.  \\nLadda ner den idag fr\xe5n Mac App Store och ta kontroll \xf6ver dina LEGO\xae-skapelser som aldrig f\xf6rr!\\n\\n<MacAppStoreBadge/>"},{"id":"/2025/05/17/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/17/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-17-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","description":"Descriere","date":"2025-05-17T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.97,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.9","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/06/3/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/10/post"}},"content":"### Descriere\\n\\nAceast\u0103 actualizare \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021be\u0219te suportul pentru tablete, adaug\u0103 pagini utile de testare \u0219i remediaz\u0103 mai multe probleme de compatibilitate \u0219i performan\u021b\u0103.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Modific\u0103ri\\n\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat layout pentru tablete** pentru o utilizare mai eficient\u0103 a ecranelor mari.\\n- **Remediat\u0103 o eroare \xeen care blocul \u201ebuton hub ap\u0103sat\u201d** ap\u0103rea pentru hub-uri care nu accept\u0103 aceast\u0103 ac\u021biune. De asemenea, au fost corectate **blocurile de senzor de culoare** afi\u0219ate incorect pentru hub-uri nesuportate (ex: BuWizz).\\n- **Remediat\u0103 o eroare \xeen care blocul \u201epornire motor\u201d** nu func\u021biona cu motoarele f\u0103r\u0103 encodere, din cauza lipsei comenzilor alternative de rulare.\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 o pagin\u0103 pentru testarea butoanelor de gamepad.**\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 o pagin\u0103 de testare a hub-urilor**, cu un panou care afi\u0219eaz\u0103 informa\u021bii, dispozitive conectate la porturi \u0219i starea de \u201eshake\u201d a porturilor.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 interpretarea incorect\u0103 a datelor de accelerometru** pentru BuWizz 2 \u0219i 3, care ducea la erori \xeen citirea orient\u0103rii.\\n- **Corectate scurgeri de memorie RAM** care duceau la \xeenchiderea aplica\u021biei pe unele dispozitive, din cauza utiliz\u0103rii excesive a memoriei.\\n- **Remediate erori la \xeenc\u0103rcarea profilelor**, care anterior puteau cauza pr\u0103bu\u0219irea aplica\u021biei \xeen anumite scenarii.\\n- **Remediat\u0103 o eroare pe Android** \xeen care eliberarea stick-urilor gamepad-ului nu reseta valorile axelor la zero."},{"id":"/2025/05/10/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/10/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-05-10-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","description":"Descriere","date":"2025-05-10T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.97,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/17/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.2 - 2025.1.3","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/19/post"}},"content":"### Descriere\\n\\nAceast\u0103 actualizare \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021be\u0219te suportul pentru tablete, adaug\u0103 pagini utile de testare \u0219i corecteaz\u0103 mai multe probleme de compatibilitate \u0219i performan\u021b\u0103.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Modific\u0103ri\\n\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat un layout pentru tablete** pentru o mai bun\u0103 utilizare a ecranelor mai mari.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare \xeen care blocul \u201ebuton hub ap\u0103sat\u201d** ap\u0103rea pentru hub-uri care nu suport\u0103 aceast\u0103 ac\u021biune. De asemenea, au fost corectate **blocurile de senzor de culoare** nepotrivite pentru hub-uri nesuportate (ex: BuWizz).\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare \xeen care blocul \u201epornire motor\u201d** nu afecta motoarele f\u0103r\u0103 encodere din cauza lipsei comenzilor alternative de rulare.\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 o pagin\u0103 pentru testarea butoanelor de gamepad.**\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 o pagin\u0103 de testare a hub-urilor**, cu un panou ce afi\u0219eaz\u0103 informa\u021bii, dispozitive conectate la porturi \u0219i statusul de \u201eshake\u201d al porturilor.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 interpretarea incorect\u0103 a datelor de la accelerometru** pentru BuWizz 2 \u0219i 3, care ducea la citiri gre\u0219ite ale orient\u0103rii.\\n- **Corectate scurgeri de memorie RAM** care provocau \xeenchiderea aplica\u021biei pe unele dispozitive din cauza utiliz\u0103rii ridicate a memoriei.\\n- **Corectate erori la \xeenc\u0103rcarea profilelor** care anterior provocau pr\u0103bu\u0219irea aplica\u021biei \xeen anumite scenarii.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare pe Android** \xeen care eliberarea stick-urilor de la gamepad nu reseta valorile axelor la zero."},{"id":"/2025/04/19/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/19/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-19-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.2 - 2025.1.3","description":"Descriere","date":"2025-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.48,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.2 - 2025.1.3","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.4","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/05/10/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.1","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/14/post"}},"content":"### Descriere\\n\\nAceast\u0103 actualizare introduce noi op\u021biuni de personalizare pentru joystick, \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021biri ale interfe\u021bei \u0219i corecturi importante pentru stabilitate.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Modific\u0103ri\\n\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare \xeen selectorul de colec\u021bii din paleta de blocuri**: selectarea unei colec\u021bii, derularea c\u0103tre alta \u0219i revenirea nu aveau niciun efect.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o pr\u0103bu\u0219ire la \xeenc\u0103rcarea profilelor complexe**, care con\u021bineau un num\u0103r mare de blocuri.\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 proprietatea \u201eTip axe\u201d** \xeen set\u0103rile joystick-ului pentru a suporta **modul pe o singur\u0103 ax\u0103** (X, Y, XY).\\n- **Ad\u0103ugat\u0103 colorizare** pentru controllerele tip volan (\u201eGMZ\u201d, \u201eNo Mercy\u201d).\\n- **Ad\u0103uga\u021bi blocuri de tip \u201eeste ap\u0103sat\u201d** pentru volane \u0219i pedale."},{"id":"/2025/04/14/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/14/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-14-post.md","title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.1","description":"Descriere","date":"2025-04-14T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.52,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.1","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.2 - 2025.1.3","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/19/post"},"nextItem":{"title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/04/post"}},"content":"### Descriere\\n\\nAceast\u0103 actualizare include mai multe corecturi importante de erori care \xeembun\u0103t\u0103\u021besc performan\u021ba, reduc consumul bateriei \u0219i optimizeaz\u0103 comportamentul blocurilor \xeen mediul de programare.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n---\\n\\n### Modific\u0103ri\\n\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare care cauza utilizare ridicat\u0103 a CPU-ului, desc\u0103rcare rapid\u0103 a bateriei \u0219i performan\u021b\u0103 sc\u0103zut\u0103.**\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare \xeen blocurile pentru gamepad** (de ex., \u201eeste butonul ap\u0103sat\u201d, \u201eeste ap\u0103sat butonul D-PAD\u201d) **care \xeempiedica ata\u0219area acestora la alte blocuri.**\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o problem\u0103 \xeen blocul de eveniment \u201ecomutator cu pa\u0219i\u201d** care gestiona incorect evenimentele tactile \u0219i num\u0103rarea pa\u0219ilor.\\n- **Corectat\u0103 o eroare \xeen blocul de list\u0103 \u201eelement din\u201d** care permitea ata\u0219area unui singur bloc ca index de argument."},{"id":"/2025/04/04/post","metadata":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/04/post","source":"@site/i18n/ro/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2025-04-04-post.md","title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","description":"\ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.0 Test Beta \xcenchis a \xcenceput!","date":"2025-04-04T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Dev","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/dev","description":"Development news"},{"inline":false,"label":"Test","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/tags/test","description":"Testing news"}],"readingTime":0.3,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Maxim","title":"Developer","url":"https://github.com/llOzzeell","page":{"permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/authors/maxim"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/llOzzeell"},"imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/45766241?v=4","key":"maxim"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"MOCPilot 2025.1.0","authors":["maxim"],"tags":["dev","test"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Lansare MOCPilot 2025.1.1","permalink":"/mocpilot-app/ro/blog/2025/04/14/post"}},"content":"## \ud83d\ude80 MOCPilot 2025.1.0 Test Beta \xcenchis a \xcenceput!\\n\\nSuntem \xeenc\xe2nta\u021bi s\u0103 anun\u021b\u0103m c\u0103 testul beta \xeenchis pentru MOCPilot 2025 este acum activ! Utilizatorii selecta\u021bi pot explora noile func\u021bionalit\u0103\u021bi, pot oferi feedback \u0219i pot contribui la modelarea viitorului aplica\u021biei MOCPilot.\\n\\n\x3c!-- truncate --\x3e\\n\\nDac\u0103 ai primit o invita\u021bie, verific\u0103-\u021bi emailul pentru detaliile de acces.  \\n\xce\u021bi mul\u021bumim c\u0103 faci parte din aceast\u0103 etap\u0103 important\u0103!"}]}}')}}]);